Visit us @rdgterminalmkt and pick up @metropolitanbakery bread! Level up your meals with bread baked fresh daily-literally baked today!!-It makes all of the difference!! From Baguette (French and Whole Wheat), to Levain, a robust sourdough, and French Table Bread, a versatile light bread to be enjoyed with any meal-we’ve got you covered! *We carry a full selection of Metropolitan Bread at our Reading Terminal Location, the selection at Elkins Park may vary. We’ll happily slice any loaf for you on our bread slicer, or enjoy it whole!
